data.description: This home is a must see located in the Country Club Addition with easy access to Highway 7. Beautiful updated Kitchen with double oven, granite countertops, large breakfast bar and so much more. This unique home offers a separate dining room, a sunroom, spacious renovated bathrooms, a sprinkler system, large backyard front and back with new privacy fence installed in 2022 . Plus, there is a detached garage with two attached storage areas and a separate long driveway with more covered parking in the back. More extras include a storm cellar. Genrac Generator and a water softener with a filtration system too!!
